Directions for the Busts76
4one of Alexr the Greatanother of Julius Csaranr of Chs 12 Sweeden & a 4th of the King Prussia.
N.B.these are not to exceed 15 Inchs in hight nor 10 in width for brokn Pedimt.
2 other Busts of Prince Eugene & the Duke Of Marlborhsomewht smallr. 2 Wild Beastsnot to exceed 12 Inch in highth nor18 in length. Sundry Small Ornaments for Chim[ne]y piece.77

